notification.title: U ETS Market Vibe by EU Carbon Team / 03 Jan 2020 / 07:00 CET
notification.message: Next week, the first auctions in 2020 will be held. As 6 January is a public holiday in Germany and other member states, the first auction, worth 3.1m EUAs on behalf of the EU, will be held on 7 January.
